name: Age Defender Moisturizer
tagline: Firming, lifting, anti-wrinkle treatment for men

ingredients.Adenosine\u00a0: derived from yeast fermentation, is known to build collagen* in skin to help reduce lines and wrinkles.

ingredients.Cypress Extract\u00a0: originated from the island La Reunion (Indian Ocean) and is cultivated on protected slopes. In the formula it helps to strengthen skin.

ingredients.The strengthening protein blend: in the formula helps firm skin and improve its resiliency and elasticity.
